\id 1JN - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h 1 Johana
\toc1 Johana Mokwongo
\toc2 1 Johana
\toc3 1Joh
\mt1 1 Johana
\c 1
\s1 Wach mar ngima
\p 
\v 1 Wandikonu kuom Wach mar ngima, mane nitie nyaka aa chakruok, ma wasewinjo kendo waseneno gi wengewa, kendo waserange maber mi wamule gi lwetewa.
\v 2 Ngimani nofwenyore mine wanene, omiyo wawuoyo kuome, kendo wanyisou wach ngima mochwere mane nigi Wuoro kendo mane onyiswa.
\v 3 Wanyisou gima waseneno kendo winjo, mondo un bende ubed e achiel kodwa e lalruok. To lalruok marwa ni e kindwa gi Wuoro kod Wuode, Yesu Kristo.
\v 4 Wandikonu wachni mondo morwa obed mogundho kendo moromo chuth.
\s1 Wuotho e ler
\p 
\v 5 Puonj mane wayudo kuom Kristo kendo koro wanyisou ema: Nyasaye en ler, kendo mudho onge kuome kata matin.
\v 6 Omiyo ka wawacho ni wan e winjruok kode to pod wawuotho e mudho to wariambo kendo ok wawuothi e adiera.
\v 7 To ka wawuotho e ler, kaka en bende enie ler to wan e lalruok ngʼato gi ngʼato, kendo remb Yesu Wuode pwodhowa kuom richowa duto.
\p 
\v 8 Ka wawacho ni waonge richo, to wawuondore kendwa wawegi, kendo adiera onge e chunywa.
\v 9 To ka wahulo richowa, to oweyonwagi kendo opwodhowa kuom timbe duto ma ok odhi kare nikech en Ja-adiera kendo otimo gima kare.
\v 10 Ka wawacho ni pok watimo richo to wamiyo odoko ja-miriambo kendo wachne onge gi thuolo e ngimawa.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Nyithinda mahero, andikonu wechegi mondo kik utim richo. To ka ngʼato otimo richo, to wan gi Jabura machwakowa kendo kwayonwa Wuoro; Jali en Yesu Kristo, Ngʼat Makare.
\v 2 En e misango magolo richowa, to ok marwa kende, to nyaka richo mar piny ngima.
\p 
\v 3 Ka warito chike Nyasaye eka wabedo gi ratiro ni wangʼeye.
\v 4 To ngʼat mawacho ni ongʼeye to ok tim gima odwaro en ja-miriambo kendo adiera onge e chunye.
\v 5 To ka ngʼato orito chike Nyasaye to hera moherogo Nyasaye nenore kuome ratiro. To ma e kaka wanyalo bedo gi adiera ni wan ei Nyasaye:
\v 6 Ngʼat mawacho ni en ei Nyasaye nyaka kit ngimane mapile chal gi mar Yesu.
\p 
\v 7 Joherana, chik ma andikonuni ok en manyien. En chik musebedogo nyaka aa chakruok. Chikno en e wach ma usewinjo.
\v 8 To kata kamano, andikonu chik manyien kendo adierane nenore kuom Kristo kaachiel kodu, nikech mudho aa to ler mar adier koro rieny.
\p 
\v 9 Ngʼato angʼata mawacho niwuotho e ler to mon gi wadgi pod osiko e mudho.
\v 10 Ngʼat mohero owadgi to odak e ler, kendo ngʼama kamano onge obadho manyalo miyo ochwanyre.
\v 11 Ngʼat mamon gi owadgi to ni e mudho, kendo mudho nogo ema owuothoe, kokia kuma odhiye, nikech mudho odino wangʼe.
\q1 
\v 12 Andikonu un nyithinda mageno
\q2 nikech osewenu richou, kuom nying Yesu.
\q1 
\v 13 Andikonu un wuone
\q2 nikech ungʼeyo Jalno mane nitie nyaka aa chakruok.
\q1 Andikonu, un jomatindo,
\q2 nikech useloyo ngʼama rach.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Andikonu un nyithindo mageno
\q2 nikech ungʼeyo Wuoro.
\q1 Andikonu un wuone,
\q2 nikech ungʼeyo Jalno mane nitie nyaka aa chakruok.
\q1 Andikonu un jomatindo,
\q2 nikech utegno,
\q2 kendo wach Nyasaye odak e chunyu,
\q2 kendo useloyo ngʼama rach.
\s1 Kik uher piny
\p 
\v 15 Kik uher piny kata gimoro amora manie pinyni. Ka ngʼato ohero piny, to hera mar Wuoro onge e iye.
\v 16 Nimar gik moko duto manie piny, kaka gombo mar wangʼ kendo gombo mar ringruok kod sunga ma ji sungorego kuom gik ma gin-go, ok aa kuom Wuoro, to gin mana mag pinyni.
\v 17 Pinyni kaachiel gi gombo duto kadho, to ngʼat matimo dwach Nyasaye nobed mangima nyaka chiengʼ.
\s1 Siem kuom wasik Kristo
\p 
\v 18 Nyithinda mageno, giko chiegni kendo kaka usewinjo ni jasik Kristo biro, koro wasik Kristo mangʼeny osefwenyore. Ma e kaka wangʼeyo ni giko chiegni.
\v 19 Chutho, jogi ne oa irwa to ne ok gin jowa. Nikech ka dine gin jowa to dine gisiko kodwa, nimar dhigino nyiso malongʼo ni onge kata ngʼato achiel kuomgi mane ngʼatwa.
\p 
\v 20 Un ema Ngʼama Maler osewirou omiyo ungʼeyo adiera.
\v 21 Omiyo koro andikonu ok nikech ukia adiera, to nikech ungʼeye, kendo nikech ungʼeyo ni onge miriambo mawuok e adiera.
\v 22 Ja-miriambo to kara en ngʼa? En ngʼama wacho ni Yesu ok en Kristo. Ngʼatno e Jasik Kristo, nikech odagi Wuoro kaachiel gi Wuowi.
\v 23 Ngʼama odagi Wuowi odagi Wuoro bende, to ngʼama orwake nigi Wuoro bende.
\p 
\v 24 Kuom mano, neuru ni urito gima ne ukwongo winjo nyaka aa chakruok. Ka usiko ukano gima ne uwinjo mokwongo, to ubiro siko e winjruok gi Wuowi kod Wuoro.
\v 25 To ma e gima Kristo owuon nosingore ni nomiwa, ma en ngima mochwere.
\p 
\v 26 Andikonu wechegi kuom jogo matemo mondo owuondu.
\v 27 Un to Roho mane Kristo omiyou osewirou, omiyo ok uchando ngʼat mapuonjou. To kaka Roho museyudono puonjou kuom gik moko duto, kendo dak ma Roho odak godo e iwu en adiera ma ok miriambo mana kaka osepuonjouno, sikuru kuome.
\s1 Nyithind Nyasaye
\p 
\v 28 Omiyo koro nyithinda mageno, sikuru kuome mondo ka ofwenyore to wabed gi chir kendo maonge wichkuot e nyime ka obiro.
\p 
\v 29 Ka ungʼeyo ni Kristo en ngʼama kare to onego ungʼe bende ni ngʼato ka ngʼato matimo gima kare en nyathi Nyasaye.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Mano kaka hera ma Wuoro oherowago duongʼ kuom luongowa ni nyithind Nyasaye. Kendo mano e gima wan! Gimomiyo piny, ok ongʼeyowa en nikech piny ne ok ongʼeye.
\v 2 Osiepena mageno, koro wan nyithind Nyasaye, to kaka wabiro bedo achien pok ongʼere. To wangʼeyo ni ka Kristo nofwenyre, to wanabed machal kode, nikech wananene kaka ochal.
\v 3 Ngʼato ka ngʼato man-gi genoni pwodhore owuon mondo osik koler mana kaka en bende oler.
\p 
\v 4 Ji matimo richo ketho chik; chutho, richo en ketho chik.
\v 5 To ungʼeyo ni Kristo nobiro mondo ogol richowa. Ungʼeyo bende ni richo onge kuome.
\v 6 Ngʼat man kuom Kristo ok sik katimo richo. Ngʼat mosiko katimo richo pok onene kendo okiaye.
\p 
\v 7 Nyithinda mageno, kik uyie ngʼato wuondu. Ngʼat matimo gima kare en ngʼama kare, mana kaka en bende en ngʼama kare.
\v 8 Ngʼat mosiko katimo richo en ngʼat Satan, nikech Satan osiko katimo richo nyaka aa chakruok. Gimomiyo Wuod Nyasaye nobiro ne en ni mondo otiek tich Satan.
\v 9 Ngʼama Nyasaye onywolo ok dhi nyime katimo richo, nikech kit Nyasaye osiko kuome. Ok onyal timo richo onywole kuom Nyasaye.
\v 10 Kaka wanyalo ngʼeyo pogruok manie kind nyithind Nyasaye gi nyithind Satan ema: Ngʼat ma ok tim gima kare kendo ma ok ohero owadgi ok en nyathi Nyasaye.
\s1 Herreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato
\p 
\v 11 Wach mane uwinjo nyaka aa chakruok ema: Nyaka waherreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato.
\v 12 Kik wachal gi Kain mane en koth ngʼama rach, omiyo nonego owadgi mahie. To nonego owadgi nangʼo? Nonego owadgi nikech timbene ne richo, to timbe owadgi ne ni kare.
\v 13 Kuom mano, owetena kik ubwogi ka jopiny mon kodu.
\v 14 Wangʼeyo ni wasekalo waa e tho miwadonjo e ngima, nikech wahero owetewa. Ngʼama ok ohero owadgi osiko e tho.
\v 15 Ngʼama mon gi owadgi en janek, to ungʼeyo ni janek onge gi ngima mochwere.
\p 
\v 16 Ma e kaka wangʼeyo gima hera en; Kristo nochiwonwa ngimane. Wan bende onego wachiw ngimawa ni owetewa.
\v 17 Ka ngʼato jamoko to oneno owadgi kochando to ok okeche, ere kaka ngʼama kamano nyalo wacho ni en gihera mar Nyasaye?
\v 18 Nyithinda mageno, kik wawach mana gi dhowa ni wahero ji, to waher ji gi tim kendo gi adiera.
\p 
\v 19 Mano e yo ma wangʼeyogo ni wachungʼ e adiera, kendo mabiro miyo chunywa bed gi chir e nyim Nyasaye
\v 20 sa moro amora ma chunywa ngʼadonwa bura. Nikech Nyasaye duongʼ moloyo chunywa, kendo ongʼeyo gik moko duto.
\v 21 Omiyo, osiepega mageno, ka chunywa ok ngʼadnwa bura to wan gi chir e nyim Nyasaye.
\v 22 To wayudo koa kuome, gimoro amora mwakwaye nikech wamako chikene kendo watimo gik mamore.
\v 23 To ma e chik Nyasaye: ni mondo wayie e nying Wuode Yesu Kristo kendo mondo waherre ngʼato gi ngʼato, mana kaka Kristo nochikowa.
\v 24 Joma orito chike Nyasaye ni kuome to en bende en kuomgi. To ma e kaka wangʼeyo ni Nyasaye odak eiwa: Wangʼeyo nikech Roho ma osemiyowa.
\c 4
\s1 Roho mar adier gi roho mar miriambo
\p 
\v 1 Osiepena mageno kik uyie roho duto, to temgiuru mondo ufwenygi ka bende gia kuom Nyasaye nikech jonabi mag miriambo mathoth osebiro e piny koni gi koni.
\v 2 Ma e kaka unyalo ngʼeyo Roho mar Nyasaye: Roho ma hulo ni Yesu Kristo nobiro e ringruok en Roho moa kuom Nyasaye,
\v 3 to roho moro amora makwedo Yesu ok en Roho mar Nyasaye. Chuny ma kamano en mar Jasik Kristo ma usewinjo ni onego bi kendo makoro ni e piny kata sani.
\p 
\v 4 Nyithinda mageno, un to un nyithind Nyasaye kendo useloyo jonabi mag miriambogo, nikech Jal manie iu duongʼ moloyo Jal manie piny.
\v 5 Gin jopiny, omiyo giwuoyo kuom pinyni kendo piny winjogi.
\v 6 Wan to wan jo-Nyasaye omiyo joma ongʼeyo Nyasaye winjowa, to ngʼat ma ok ngʼat Nyasaye ok winjwa. Ma e yo mwangʼeyogo Roho mar adier gi Roho mar miriambo.
\s1 Hera mar Nyasaye
\p 
\v 7 Osiepena mageno waherreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato nikech hera aa kuom Nyasaye. Ngʼat man gihera en nyathi Nyasaye kendo ongʼeyo Nyasaye.
\v 8 Ngʼat maonge hera kia Nyasaye, nikech Nyasaye en hera.
\v 9 Nyasaye nonyiso hera moherowago kama: Ne ooro Wuode ma miderma e piny mondo wabed mangima kuome.
\v 10 Ma e gima hera en: ok ni wan ema ne wahero Nyasaye, to Nyasaye ema noherowa mokwongo mi nooro Wuode kaka misango mar richowa.
\v 11 Osiepena mageno, ka Nyasaye noherowa kamano, to wan bende waherre ngʼato gi ngʼato.
\v 12 Onge ngʼama oseneno Nyasaye, to ka waherore ngʼato gi ngʼato to Nyasaye odak eiwa, kendo herane chopo kare eiwa.
\p 
\v 13 Wangʼeyo ni wadak ei Nyasaye kendo en bende en eiwa, nikech osemiyowa Rohone.
\v 14 Waseneno kendo wanyiso ji ni Wuoro oseoro Wuode mondo obed Jawar mar piny.
\v 15 Ka ngʼato ohulo ni Yesu en wuod Nyasaye, to Nyasaye odak e iye kendo en bende odak ei Nyasaye.
\v 16 Omiyo koro wangʼeyo kendo wageno kuom hera ma Nyasaye oherowago.
\p Nyasaye en hera. Ngʼato mosiko e hera osiko kuom Nyasaye, kendo Nyasaye bende odak kuome.
\v 17 Ma e kaka herawa nyaka nyisre chuth mondo chiengʼ ngʼado bura wabed gi chir nikech e ngima mar pinyni wachal kode.
\v 18 Luoro onge e hera; hera mar adier riembo luoro oko nikech luoro ema kelo kum. Ngʼat man-gi luoro pok ochopo e hera mar adier.
\p 
\v 19 Wan gihera nikech Nyasaye noherowa mokwongo.
\v 20 Ka ngʼato wacho ni ohero Nyasaye to omon gi wadgi to en ja-miriambo; nikech ngʼama ok ohero wadgi, moseneno gi wangʼe, ok nyal hero Nyasaye mapok oneno.
\v 21 Chik ma osemiyowa en ma: Ngʼat mohero Nyasaye nyaka her wadgi bende.
\c 5
\s1 Yie kuom Wuod Nyasaye
\p 
\v 1 Ngʼato ka ngʼato moyie ni Yesu e Kristo en nyathi Nyasaye, kendo ngʼama ohero Wuoro ohero nyathine bende.
\v 2 Ma e kaka wangʼeyo ni wahero nyithind Nyasaye: Ka wahero Nyasaye kendo wamako chikene.
\v 3 Hero Nyasaye en luoro chikene, to chikene ok tek rito
\v 4 nikech ngʼat ma Nyasaye onywolo loyo piny. Loch ma waloyogo piny en yie.
\v 5 En ngʼa moloyo piny? Mana ngʼat moyie ni Yesu en Wuod Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 6 Yesu Kristo e Jal mane obiro gi pi kod remo. Ne ok obiro gi pi kende, to nobiro gi pi kod remo. Roho Maler wacho ni ma en adieri, nikech Roho en e adiera.
\v 7 Nimar nitie joneno adek, ma gin:
\v 8 \f + \fr 5:7-8 \ft Ndiko mamoko ma bangʼe mag loko mag dho Latin ne onge gi wechegi, \fqa Timo neno koa e polo ni ji adekgi gin gimoro achiel \fv 8 \fqa Kendo nitiere gik moko adek matimo neno e piny: \ft (gik moko adekgi ne ok ondik e loko mar dho jo-Yunani kapok ochopo higa mar 1400 Bangʼ nywol Yesu).\f*Roho gi pi kod remo, kendo jonenogi winjore kuom wachni.
\v 9 Wayie gi nend dhano, to nend Nyasaye ema duongʼ moloyo nikech en neno ma Nyasaye owuon osewacho kuom Wuode.
\v 10 Ngʼat moyie kuom Wuod Nyasaye nigi nenoni e chunye, to ngʼama ok oyie kuome miyo Nyasaye doko ja-miriambo, nikech odagi yie gima Nyasaye osewacho kaka janeno kuom Wuode.
\v 11 To ma e gima Nyasaye osewacho: Nyasaye osemiyowa ngima mochwere kendo ngimano ni kuom wuode.
\v 12 Ngʼat man-gi Wuowi nigi ngima; to ngʼat maonge gi Wuod Nyasaye onge gi ngima.
\s1 Weche mogik
\p 
\v 13 Andikonu wechegi, un joma oyie kuom nying Wuod Nyasaye, mondo ungʼe ni un gi ngima mochwere.
\v 14 Ma e chir ma wan-go ka wadhi e nyim Nyasaye ni ka wakwaye gimoro mowinjore gi dwache to owinjowa.
\v 15 To ka wangʼeyo ni owinjowa kwakwaye gimoro, to wangʼeyo ni waseyudo gima wakwayono.
\p 
\v 16 Ka ngʼato oneno wadgi katimo richo ma ok tere e tho, to owinjore olamne mondo Nyasaye omi ngʼatno ngima. Awuoyo kuom joma richogi ok tergi e tho. To nitie richo matero ji e tho; ma ok awach ni olamie Nyasaye.
\v 17 Ketho duto gin richo, to nitie richo ma ok ter ji e tho.
\p 
\v 18 Wangʼeyo ni ngʼama Nyasaye onywolo ok sik katimo richo, nikech Wuod Nyasaye orite kendo ngʼama rach ok nyal mule.
\v 19 Wangʼeyo ni wan nyithind Nyasaye, kendo piny duto ni e bwo loch mar ngʼama rach.
\v 20 Wangʼeyo bende ni Wuod Nyasaye osebiro kendo osemiyowa rieko mar winjo tiend wach, mondo wangʼe ngʼat ma ja-adiera, ngʼat makoro wanie iye, en wuode Yesu Kristo. En e Nyasaye madier kendo en e ngima mochwere.
\b
\b
\p 
\v 21 Nyithinda mageno, tangʼuru ni nyiseche manono ma dhano oloso.
